---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Icon from '../../components/Icon.astro';
import InstitutionLogo from '../../components/InstitutionLogo.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="履歷" description="個人履歷" locale="zh-hk">
  <section class="section-light cv-document-shell">
    <div class="container cv-document-container">
      <header class="cv-document-header">
        <div class="cv-header-main">
          <h1 class="cv-name">郭雨澤</h1>
          <p class="cv-role"><InstitutionLogo src="/assets/logos/institutions/whu.png">武漢大學</InstitutionLogo>物理學本科生 · 2026 年秋季擬入學 <InstitutionLogo src="/assets/logos/institutions/pku.png">北京大學</InstitutionLogo>天體物理博士</p>
          <p class="cv-focus">研究方向：高能天體物理、引力波、宇宙學與多信使天文學。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cv-header-links">
          <a class="cv-quick-link" href="mailto:guoyuze@whu.edu.cn"><span class="icon icon-envelope-asset" aria-hidden="true"></span>郵箱</a>
          <a class="cv-quick-link" href="https://github.com/ryan-gwo" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GitHub</a>
          <a class="cv-quick-link" href="/assets/pdf/zh-hk/cv_hk.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><Icon name="download" />PDF</a>
          <a class="cv-quick-link" href="/zh-hk/">返回首頁</a>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="cv-document-layout">
        <main class="cv-main" aria-label="CV 內容">
          <section class="cv-section" aria-labelledby="education-title">
            <h2 id="education-title">教育經歷</h2>
            <ol class="cv-timeline">
              <li class="cv-item">
                <div class="cv-item-head">
                  <h3><InstitutionLogo src="/assets/logos/institutions/pku.png">北京大學</InstitutionLogo> · 天體物理學博士（擬）</h3>
                  <p class="cv-item-meta">北京 · 預計 2026 年秋季起</p>
                </div>
                <p>擬在北京大學物理學院天文學系繼續開展博士階段研究。</p>
              </li>
              <li class="cv-item">
                <div class="cv-item-head">
                  <h3><InstitutionLogo src="/assets/logos/institutions/whu.png">武漢大學</InstitutionLogo> · 物理學學士</h3>
                  <p class="cv-item-meta">武漢 · 2022-2026</p>
                </div>
                <p>核心課程：理論力學、電動力學、量子力學、統計物理、數學物理方法、群論、普通天文學、天體物理。</p>
              </li>
            </ol>
          </section>

          <section class="cv-section" aria-labelledby="interests-title">
            <h2 id="interests-title">研究興趣</h2>
            <ul class="cv-bullets">
              <li>高能天體物理</li>
              <li>引力波天文學</li>
              <li>宇宙學</li>
              <li>多信使天文學</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="cv-section" aria-labelledby="research-title">
            <h2 id="research-title">研究經歷 / 項目</h2>
            <ol class="cv-timeline">
              <li class="cv-item">
                <div class="cv-item-head">
                  <h3>天文競賽驅動的系統訓練</h3>
                  <p class="cv-item-meta">2019-2021</p>
                </div>
                <p>通過高階天文競賽訓練建立天文與天體物理基礎，重點強化定量建模與觀測問題分析能力。</p>
              </li>
              <li class="cv-item">
                <div class="cv-item-head">
                  <h3>本科階段天體物理方向深化</h3>
                  <p class="cv-item-meta">2022-至今</p>
                </div>
                <p>在武漢大學持續進行天體物理與宇宙學方向學習，圍繞引力波及相關課題準備博士階段研究。</p>
              </li>
            </ol>
          </section>

          <section class="cv-section" aria-labelledby="awards-title">
            <h2 id="awards-title">榮譽與獎項</h2>
            <ul class="cv-awards">
              <li><span class="cv-award-year">2024</span><span class="cv-award-text">國家獎學金，中華人民共和國教育部</span></li>
              <li><span class="cv-award-year">2024</span><span class="cv-award-text">中國科學院國家天文台獎學金，中國科學院國家天文台</span></li>
              <li><span class="cv-award-year">2021</span><span class="cv-award-text">IOAA 金牌，國際天文與天體物理奧林匹克競賽</span></li>
              <li><span class="cv-award-year">2020</span><span class="cv-award-text">CNAO 金牌，全國中學生天文知識競賽</span></li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="cv-section" aria-labelledby="skills-title">
            <h2 id="skills-title">技能</h2>
            <ul class="cv-bullets">
              <li>LaTeX：學術寫作、文檔排版與參考文獻管理</li>
              <li>扎實的數學與物理問題求解訓練</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="cv-section" aria-labelledby="languages-title">
            <h2 id="languages-title">語言</h2>
            <ul class="cv-bullets">
              <li>中文（母語）</li>
              <li>英語（流利）</li>
            </ul>
          </section>
        </main>

        <aside class="cv-side" aria-label="概要信息">
          <section class="cv-side-card">
            <h2>當前身份</h2>
            <ul class="cv-side-list">
              <li>武漢大學物理學本科生</li>
              <li>擬攻讀北京大學天體物理博士</li>
              <li>所在地：中國湖北武漢</li>
            </ul>
          </section>
          <section class="cv-side-card">
            <h2>研究關鍵詞</h2>
            <ul class="cv-side-list">
              <li>Astrophysics</li>
              <li>Gravitational Waves</li>
              <li>Cosmology</li>
              <li>Multi-messenger Astronomy</li>
            </ul>
          </section>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>